        <mxCell id="a89" value="C*" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#222;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=9;" edge="1" parent="1" source="b8" target="b9">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
